content:
Ee newsletter/blog enduko explanation idi Mukhya Gamanika! Naaku inka clarity ledu. This is a work in progress Entidi? 🤷‍♀️ # Telugu bhasha kapadataniki nuva tharam vaipu nundi vasthunna prayatnam Antha scene lekapoyina, manam alage feel avvali. Kani, this is just for us to have fun 😎. 💵 Akkada varaku velthe 🤔, maybe monetize cheddam.
Verticals(🍾) # News 🗞 # Udaharanaki: Weekly okasari, news pampabothunnamu(bahusa sunday podunna). Categories manam discuss cheyachu.
Business/World News 💸 # Mana Sahaja garu World news mariyu Business news try chesthanu ani mata ivvadam jarigindi. Tech/Space News ✈ # Ee articles kosam Shashank krushi cheyadaniki sidhanga unnadu. Laddu garu, Pappu garu sahayam chestharani thanu entho assisthunnadu. Subhavarthalu 😊🌈🦄 # Idi Sneha gari churukaina alochana. Varthalalo unna bad news tho visigipoyi unna valla kosam rayabothunna section idi. Blog # Lifestyle 💹 # Maroka goppa alochana tho andariki current trends gurinchi rayabothunnadi Sneha. Bhala bhala! Movie reviews 🎥 # Deeniki Sahiti garu, Laddu garu, Pappu garu ayithene nyayam cheyagalugutharani, ekagreevanga nirnayinchabadinadi. Picha Vaagudu # Idi nenu vivaristhe topic ki nyayam cheyalenu. Anduke Sneha garini sampradinchandi. Misc # Memes # Andaru cheyyi vesthe addiripothundi 🤘 Enduku Cheyyali? ⁉ # Brownie points kosam 🍪🍪🍪. Endukante Ee website revenue generate cheyyatledu kabatti. Dabbulu eppudu ille(Pappu 😉)
Comedy cheyadaniki reason avasaram ledu. Paiga, chala mandi chethuvutharani naa abhiprayam.

title: Enduku? Emiti? Ela?
